@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_affsxz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.27) + (v0 + 0.03 / tmp + 0.29)) + wp.abs(wp.abs(v2 + 0.72)))
    tmp = (v0 * ((tmp + 0.90 / v2 + 0.86) * (v0 + 0.05 + v1 + 0.50)))
    tmp = wp.abs(v2)
    v1 = wp.sin(wp.cos(wp.abs(tmp + 0.96)))
    data[tid] = v0
